To use this, simply download the entire codebase.
then in the directory with the codebase create use cmd python -m venv venv to create a virtual environment
then venv/Scripts.activate.bat to activate the environment
then pip install requirements.txt to install all python packages
then run python app.py
go to the URL, now the game is running on the local network
to access it on other computers on the local network enter the IPv4 address of the computer:5000 into the url on other computers
DOES NOT USE HTTPS, DOES NOT HAVE ADVANCED SECURITY FEATURES, DO NOT USE AS PRODUCTION CODE
